          "slidecontent": "• Always keep a human in the loop for high-impact network decisions\n• Automation fails, so build in fallback procedures from the start\n• Test before you trust\n• Blind reliance on self-healing systems can turn small faults into large outages\n• Log everything, because audit trails are your first defence when something goes wrong\n• As a next step, review your current automation policies and identify where human oversight could be strengthened"
